Package com.imaginea.mongodb.common

Interface Summary
MongoInstanceProvider Returns a MongoInstance based on method defined in its different implentations.
UserTokenInformation A Token has been defined which is randomly generated for every user.
 

Class Summary
ConfigMongoInstanceProvider Provides an Implementation for MongoInstanceProvider that provides instance of Mongo Db after reading parameters from config file for performing operations on MonogDb Resources {Db,collection,document}.
DateProvider Provides Date and Time for Logging different messages.
SessionMongoInstanceProvider Extract the MongoInstance from the which is a combination of usrname , mongoIP and mongoPort.
UserTokenInformationProvider Stroes the information about a token for a User and provides the implementation of generating tokenID.
